official_title: A resolution to express the sense of the Senate that, by the end of the 104th Congress, the Senate should pass health care legislation to provide all Americans with coverage that is at least as good as the Senate provides for itself.

summary.text: Calls for the Senate, by the end of the 104th Congress, to pass health care legislation to provide all Americans with coverage that is at least as good as the Senate provides for itself.
